{"tid":2320567,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"封殺 6 歲電競神童 Call of Duty 決定惹粉絲不滿","createTime":"2020-12-11T02:15:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T03:03:45.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3ccd211cc3fd8f44c34c1b3ddfba68881dcaf9f8","tid":2320567,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T02:15:47.000Z","msg":"⋯⋯雖然 RowdyRogan 只得 6 歲，但他不但成為了 Call of Duty World League 聯賽的最年輕參賽者，甚至在 FaZe Clan 挑戰賽晉身決賽。不過這名電競神童最近卻遇到了挫折，日前在 Twitch 進行《Call of Duty: Warzone》遊戲直播期間，他的帳號突然被遊戲商 Activision 封鎖。<br />\n<br />\n由於《Call of Duty: Warzone》在美國 ESRB 評級為 M（即成人內容），建議玩家要到 17 歲或以上才適合遊玩，而 Activision 的服務條款則表明產品提供予至少 13 歲或以上人士，但同時需遵守產品年齡等級和限制等要求，假如玩家年齡為 18 歲以下，家長或監護人要先行審視服務條款。申請 Activision 帳號本身亦要求玩家年過 18 歲，13 歲以上但未滿 18 歲則要先獲得家長同意⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/12/11/%E5%B0%81%E6%AE%BA-6-%E6%AD%B2%E9%9B%BB%E7%AB%B6%E7%A5%9E%E7%AB%A5-call-of-duty-%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A%E6%83%B9%E7%B2%89%E7%B5%B2%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF/game-channel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F12%2F11%2F%25E5%25B0%2581%25E6%25AE%25BA-6-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E9%259B%25BB%25E7%25AB%25B6%25E7%25A5%259E%25E7%25AB%25A5-call-of-duty-%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%25AE%259A%25E6%2583%25B9%25E7%25B2%2589%25E7%25B5%25B2%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF%2Fgame-channel%2F&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqaGgm0NOSfkDZSs230CVm%2Fs%3D&h=24680d58\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/12/11/%E5%B0%81%E6%AE%BA-6-%E6%AD%B2%E9%9B%BB%E7%AB%B6%E7%A5%9E%E7%AB%A5-call-of-duty-%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A%E6%83%B9%E7%B2%89%E7%B5%B2%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF/game-channel/</a>"},{"pid":"a6e21cccd9dabd06eac704cb7b285b8d9fc0eb35","tid":2320567,"uid":228894,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T02:25:41.000Z","msg":"6歲神之手指被dmm封殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96361ebb4270e92cf8286e43